reviews.text:
Food of Man Hing Brisket Offal Specialist just average, and the restaurant is not clean too.
Come here for the signature beef brisket, bit it's disappointed.  The taste of the beef brisket is not rich, and the noodle is not fresh neither.  The restaurant itself is not very clean and messy, and the booth seats are too packed to sit
The broth is full of beef flavor. If you want to try fresh beef brisket (rib parts) and beef delicacy, this is the place to go. Good value!
味道不錯 但比同類價格貴

とても、親切な店員さんでした。
お店は、キレイとは言えないけど、麺の味は薄味でさっぱりしてて、細麺。美味しかったです。
地方－般，崩沙腩正有水準和囗感
